title: Los Espookys Cast | Trump Sits Down with ABC’s George Stephanopoulos: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at President Trump sitting down for a rare interview with a network that wasn't Fox News.

Then, Julio Torres, Ana Fabrega and Fred Armisen talk about Fred’s heavy American accent when speaking Spanish, the unique jobs of their characters in Los Espookys and finding knockoff American candy in South America.

They also take a few more questions backstage at Studio 8G exclusively for this podcast.
